---
// src/layouts/TelegramLayout.astro
---

<section class="flex flex-col gap-8">
  <header class="mb-4 rounded-2xl border border-base-content/8 bg-base-100/45 px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-sm">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary/70">
      <i class="ri-quill-pen-line"></i>
      <span>Notes</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold flex items-center gap-3 tracking-tight">
      <span>拾荒笔记</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-base-content/62 mt-2 leading-relaxed">
      一些随性的记录和暂时不写成长文的想法，轻一点放在这里。
    </p>
  </header>

  <div id="dynamic-feed-container" class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <slot />
  </div>
</section>
